say.text: Wrong number. Next house down the street
This ist seventy-nine Black Mold Road, isn't it?
Yes, but... It was not me! I didn't mean... I promise
Dunno what are you talkin' about, sir. I was hired by one Mr Ripley to get a little job done and have an appointment with him.
You can bet your donkey, sir. Der very Karl Heinrich Blauschwein
But, why in the hell you introduce yourself aiming for my head with that huge gun of yours?
I'm suppossed to look like a really tough bad guy... You know, they spent all the budget in fancy and insanely expensive props and animations...
Well, sort of. So no money for hiring a decent writer. So don't expect an award-winning script this time.
I've been waiting for you all the day. The appointment was for this morning.
Es tut mir leid, mein Herr. My sister ist bedridden with bluetongue, so I had to take her place and sing the bass part in the chorus of the church, and forgot about our little business.
Okay okay. Sehr gut Herr Ripley
